gobblin.converter

Class MetadataConverterWrapper<SI,SO,DI,DO>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.converter.Converter<SI,SO,Object,RecordWithMetadata<DO>>
      • gobblin.converter.MetadataConverterWrapper<SI,SO,DI,DO>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FinalState, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class MetadataConverterWrapper<SI,SO,DI,DO>
extends Converter<SI,SO,Object,RecordWithMetadata<DO>>
    Wraps a given converter to accept a RecordWithMetadata with a given data type, convert the underlying record using the wrapped converter, and pass the metadata through untouched
